snippet.title: Granger And Amber Smith Open Up About Grief After Losing 3-Year-Old Son | TODAY All Day
snippet.description:
Country music star Granger Smith and his wife, Amber, sat down with TODAY’s Natalie Morales for an emotional interview about the day they lost their son, River, to a drowning accident. They shared their story as a warning for other parents.
